## Rollback boundary

::rollback-panel{severity="high"}
#trigger
Rollback after two failed freshness checks or a station-to-region mismatch.

#steps
1. Announce the decision.
2. Restore the previous image digest.
3. Verify one station from each region.

::code-group{label="Commands"}
```shell
deployctl rollback orbital --to 7.3.2
deployctl status orbital --watch
```

```yaml
target: orbital
expected_version: 7.3.2
checks: [north, harbor, tokyo]
```
::

#footer
:badge{tone="danger"}[Stop] Keep the rollback operator on the call until all
three checks report a stable timestamp.
::

